title: AWS re:Invent 2025 - The Agentic advantage: How AWS Partners unlock AI's full potential (PEX201)
title_cn: AWS re:Invent 2025 - 代理优势：AWS 合作伙伴如何释放 AI 的全部潜力 (PEX201)
abstract: Agentic AI introduces a new layer of intelligence: systems that don’t just predict, but act. AWS Partners play a critical role in helping customers build, integrate and scale agentic workflows. Join us as we walk through a few of the most prevelant agentic use cases from 2025 and into 2026 looking at how partners are accelerating agentic AI with AWS.
abstract_cn: 代理式AI引入了新的智能层：这些系统不仅能预测，还能采取行动。AWS合作伙伴在帮助客户构建、集成和扩展代理式工作流程方面发挥着关键作用。请加入我们，一起了解2025年至2026年最普遍的几个代理式用例，看看合作伙伴如何通过AWS加速代理式AI的发展。

presenter.name: PRIYA ARORA
presenter.title: Global Head of Data & AI Partner Programs, Data & AI Partner GTM
